article_title: Deadly accident closes part of midtown
article_text:
Tucson Police are investigating a single-vehicle crash that has now turned deadly.

The accident happened around 6:30 p.m. Sunday night near Grant and Swan. Police say westbound Grant is closed between Swan and Madelyn.

Investigators are telling people to avoid the area.
